          "description": "I had a wonderful experience at MedRite Urgent Care, thanks to Josephine. She was incredibly warm and sweet from the moment we arrived. My friend was very tense and apprehensive, and Josephine took the time to calm him down with such kindness and patience. She made him feel comfortable and safe while ensuring he received the medical care he needed. Her compassion truly made a stressful situation so much easier. Thank you, Josephine, for going above and beyond.",
