          "description": "Team was amazing. Great service. Staff all the way from the receptionist to the physician Was extremely helpful. They requested an x-ray technician to come and see me and they got here within 15 minutes. Best service I received an urgent care ever.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214eFNVdFBOQzFyYzFGSU0xZFpkbkF4WVU0d01GRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x50a9d141bee8c2ea!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmxxSUtPNC1rc1FIM1dZdnAxYU4wMFE%7C%7C?hl=en",
