          "description": "Went here years ago and I get a call from a collections agency saying I have an outstanding balance. I don\u2019t recall any mention of a balance during my visit, and why they would send it to collections without notifying me first is beyond me. Now I\u2019m trying to pay it off so my credit score isn\u2019t dinged and they are being incredibly unhelpful - taking weeks to respond to simple emails about account balances, or even just not responding after multiple inquiries. Unprofessional and very frustrating, plus this now has implications for my ability to rent, take out loans, etc, all because of a simple urgent care visit. Would recommend avoiding at all costs.",
